  	    "alternativeHeadline": "When the economy goes to pot, we the people place our faith in one indisputably sexy commodity. It\u0027s the lone bright spot on Wall Street and a rallying cry for the riotous right. So as the Ron Pauls of the world dream of a return to the gold standard, we sent our intrepid correspondent to the Klondike, where a new gold rush is on and rumors of a mother lode have everyone acting a little feverish",
  	    "url": "http://gq.com/story/gold-standard-ron-paul-gold-rush-klondike",
  	    "image": ["http://media.gq.com/photos/5582fbaa09f0bee56440c15e/master/pass/news-and-politics-2012-01-gold-gold-628.jpg"],
  	    "thumbnailUrl": "http://media.gq.com/photos/5582fbaa09f0bee56440c15e/master/pass/news-and-politics-2012-01-gold-gold-628.jpg",
